    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Refining Your Prompt\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help explore, refine, and develop your future prediction.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Refine your initial prompt to increase accuracy and reduce bias. Use the tips below to help you. \r\n2. Send your prompt to AI Chat and read its response.\r\n3. Repeat this process several times until you are satisfied with AI's prediction.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n**Tips for Better Results**\r\n- Ask the AI to predict based on current trends, research, or diverse perspectives.\r\n- Don't just accept the first answer - challenge it or ask for alternatives.\r\n- Want to make it more inclusive? Ask: _\"How might this affect different communities?\"_",
